soot.jimple.infoflow.methodSummary.data.summary

Class GapDefinition

  • java.lang.Object
    • soot.jimple.infoflow.methodSummary.data.summary.GapDefinition

  • public class GapDefinition
extends Object
    Definition of a gap in a method summary. A gap occurs if a data flow reaches a callback method which is not known to the library generation code, but must be analyzed when the summary is later used.
    Author:
    Steven Arzt
